  <md:title>AE_Lecture 5_Part C_continued_High frequency analysis of CB.</md:title>
  <md:abstract>AE_Lecture 5_Part C_CB gives  the high frequency analysis of CB Amplifier while using a common self biasing network. We can use the same self-biasing network to realize CB,CE and CC and then make a comparative study of their upper cu-off frequency.</md:abstract>
